scoringRubric.5: Peak - practices consistent, high output, high energy, notable wins
scoringRubric.4: Solid - more hits than misses, making progress, generally positive
scoringRubric.3: Mixed - some wins some losses, nothing remarkable either way
scoringRubric.2: Rough - struggled with distractions/food/energy, low output, more misses
scoringRubric.1: Hard - off track, major struggles, survival mode
